Kawadsa - कवडसा


Kawadasa, the gem in the crown of Rangawardhan calls for all the theater loving crowd this year with much more pump and pomp. Judged by experts and appreciated by all , if your college has that one act to hold the audience back on their seats and stand out of the crowd then the stage is all yours. Come and enlighten the stage with your electrifying performances. Its time to put the efforts you took with your Director, technicians and the whole team on the display

Pathanatya - पथनाट्य


With simple costumes and props, with little or no amplification of sounds, with actors depending on theirs natural vocal and physical abilities, Pathanatya, the street play competitions is the most effective mode to spread social messages. Pathanatya that takes place at the heart of VJTI, the Quadrangle has witnessed power driven performances in the past and we look forth for many more. Get your teams ready folks!

Nrutyavishkar नृत्याविष्कार


Solo/Duet/Group Dance
What unifies the mind, heart and soul ! Surely Dance! In its all forms and grandeur, dance never misses to make us spellbound. Nrutyavishkar,the solo, duet and group dance competition of Rangawardhan, honours the rich maharashtrian dance forms. Nrutyavishkar is one of the most crowd pulling compettion of Rangawardhan that is personified by grace and grandeur.
